Source: pository
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Pository Team <pository@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11), nodejs (>= 20)
Standards-Version: 4.1.4
Homepage: https://github.com/rsxdalv/pository

Package: pository
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 20)
Suggests: pository-frontend
Description: Lightweight Debian package artifact repository
 Pository is a minimal, self-hosted artifact repository for Debian packages.
 It provides REST API for uploading, downloading, listing, and deleting
 Debian packages with API key authentication and role-based access control.

Package: pository-frontend
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 20), pository
Description: Web dashboard for the Pository package repository
 A Next.js web dashboard for managing a Pository instance. Provides a
 browser-based UI for browsing packages, viewing metrics, and managing
 API keys. Runs as a separate systemd service on port 3223 by default.
